<br>
Unfortunately, about 2 beers or 2 mixed drinks into any evening and the urge to smoke becomes overwhelming at times.<br>
<br>
This past weekend was the first one in the last 6 months that I was able to party with my friends (99% of whom smoke) and not light up!<br>
<br>
Of course my nails have suffered horribly...  I've just about chewed them to nubs.<br>
<br>
The one thing that I have learned is that I have to continuously remind myself why I'm not smoking.  For me it's because I have noticed a significant reduction in lung efficiency and I don't like that at all.<br>
<br>
I don't believe in cold turkey so your method of reducing your smoking first seems to be a good plan.  Take smoking out of the easy times and then when you've got that down tackle the tough times. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=darkpaktgrimsoul>Darkpakt Grimsoul</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer</span><br>  Posts: 644<br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/10/03 1:50 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Smoking!!!!</span><hr size=1> The best way I've found to cut down on smoking is to keep yourself preoccuppied with something that doesn't allow you to smoke.  Get like a part time job to fill up your free time and it'll at least stop you from finishing a pack a day as long as you don't chain after getting off work. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=pedidustyboots>Pedi Dustyboots</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Arcanist</span><br>  Posts: 913<br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/10/03 2:18 pm)</font><br>     <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Smoking!!!!</span><hr size=1> General question: How much money a week do you spend on your smoking habits? Just curious. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=dryfft>Dryfft</A></span><br> <span class=user