When you drink, the addiction is not stronger, but the HABIT comes out in full force.<br>
<br>
Maybe when at bars, buy a couple packs of those swisher sweets, or other types of filtered cherry or whatever type of cigar you can get.  You dont inhale them but it makes you feel like your smoking to satisfy the habit part.<br>
